I know.

00:14:50.679 --> 00:14:51.679
It's not the...

00:14:51.679 --> 00:14:56.400
I just don't want everybody to have to yell across the room.

00:14:56.400 --> 00:15:06.200
We don't have one person running around with a microphone.

